{
  "texts": [
    "A novel aspect of our performance measurement is the inclusion of both execution time and diversity in the reward function, encouraging the agent to find solutions that not only increase the execution time but also explores more in search space.",
    "We refer to our PPO RL algorithms as RL PPO E when the reward function only includes execution time, and RL PPO ED when the reward function includes both execution time and diversity.",
    "Similarly, we refer to our A2C RL algorithms as RL A2C E when the reward function only includes execution time, and RL A2C ED when the reward function includes both execution time and diversity.",
    "The results for each case study is shown in the following subsections.",
    "6-DOF Case StudyIn Figure 5.5, we observe the evolution of the reward function throughout the execution of the algorithm with an A2C agent for one run when diversity is inclued in the reward function."
  ]
}